OL,3,CTroubled fire services to publish
OL,4,Cculture review findings
OL,6,FTwo troubled Welsh fire services will
OL,7,Fpublish the findings of a review into
OL,8,Ftheir culture later today.
OL,10,FIt comes after an investigation by ITV
OL,11,FWales, which saw more than 35
OL,12,Fwhistleblowers raising serious
OL,13,Fconcerns about behaviour in the
OL,14,FServices.
OL,16,FNorth Wales and Mid and West Wales
OL,17,FFire and Rescue Services are set to
OL,18,Fpublish the final reports of a jointly
OL,19,Fcommissioned Independent Culture
OL,20,FReview at 11am.
