OL,6,FAccording to the services, the review
OL,7,Fwill mark a "significant milestone in
OL,8,Fthe ongoing commitment of both Fire
OL,9,Fand Rescue Services to fostering a
OL,10,Fsupportive, inclusive and progressive
OL,11,Fworkplace culture.
OL,13,FWorkplace culture at the Welsh fire
OL,14,Fservices has been under the spotlight
OL,15,Ffor some time.
OL,17,FITV Wales revealed allegations of a
OL,18,Ftoxic culture at both North Wales Fire
OL,19,Fand Rescue Service and Mid and West
OL,20,FWales Fire and Rescue Service earlier
OL,21,Flast year.
